HEADWORD: yummy
<hw>yum"my</hw> <pr>(y⟦ucr⟧m"m⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Very
pleasing or attractive; especially, pleasing to the taste; delicious;
scrumptious.</def> <mark>[colloq.]</mark> ⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> delectable, delicious, luscious, pleasant-tasting,
scrumptious, toothsome.</syn>⟦br⟧
